Reality vs Narrative – The Netherlands is defending Greenland  
Narrative: “The Netherlands stands firm with NATO in the Arctic struggle. Full commitment against Russia and China. Flipse is our forward deployed asset.”

Reality:  
We send 1 (one) soldier.  
Flipse.  
Alone.  
Greenland = 2.1 million km².  
Flipse = 2.1 million km² per soldier.  

Germany sends 13. Still a scout group, but Flipse is out there solo on the ice with a steaming thermos of coffee and a stroopwafel:  
“Hey Putin, Xi, Trump… coffee? Stroopwafel on the side?” ☕🍪❄️

Dutch foreign policy in one sentence:  
We participate, but don’t expect anything.  

#RealityVsNarrative #greenland #FlipseTheSoldier #NATO #netherlands